---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import TextSlider from "../components/TextSlider.astro";

const title = "About | Gwen Portfolio";
---

<BaseLayout title={title}>
	<main class="about-page">
		<!-- 頁面主標題 -->
		<section class="about-intro">
			<div class="title-wrap">
				<h2><TextSlider content="About Me" /></h2>
			</div>
			<div class="content-wrap">
				<p>我是 Chen-Pei Jyuan（陳佩娟），一名專注於**品牌識別設計（Brand Identity）**與**視覺傳達（Visual Design）**的獨立設計師。</p>
				<p>擅長透過理性構築框架，感性傳遞溫度。從標誌形體、色彩系統到包裝載體，我致力於為品牌挖掘其核心價值，並轉化為具備市場共鳴與美學深度的視覺語言。</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<hr class="section-divider" />

		<!-- 服務項目與經歷 -->
		<section class="about-details">
			<div class="detail-block">
				<h3>Services</h3>
				<ul>
					<li>品牌識別系統建立 (CIS / VI Design)</li>
					<li>視覺傳達與海報視覺設計</li>
					<li>商業包裝結構與視覺設計</li>
					<li>書籍裝幀與印刷工藝規劃</li>
				</ul>
			</div>

			<div class="detail-block">
				<h3>Experience</h3>
				<ul>
					<li>Freelance Visual Designer — 2024 - Present</li>
					<li>Brand Design Agency / Senior Designer — 2022 - 2024</li>
					<li>Visual & Package Exhibition Project — 2021</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</section>
	</main>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
	.about-page {
		max-width: 1200px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 3rem 0 6rem 0;
	}

	/* 介紹區塊排版 */
	.about-intro {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr 2fr;
		gap: 2rem;
		align-items: top;
	}

	.about-intro h2 {
		margin: 0;
		font-size: 2rem;
		font-weight: 700;
	}

	.content-wrap p {
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		line-height: 1.8;
		color: #333333;
		margin-top: 0;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}

	.content-wrap p strong {
		color: #000000;
	}

	/* 分隔線 */
	.section-divider {
		border: none;
		border-top: 1px solid #E0E0E0;
		margin: 4rem 0;
	}

	/* 服務與經歷排版 */
	.about-details {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
		gap: 4rem;
	}

	.detail-block h3 {
		font-size: 1.25rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		margin-top: 0;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.05em;
	}

	.detail-block ul {
		list-style: none;
		padding: 0;
		margin: 0;
	}

	.detail-block li {
		font-size: 1rem;
		line-height: 2;
		color: #666666;
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
	}

	/* 手機版響應式 */
	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.about-page {
			padding: 2rem 1rem 4rem 1rem;
		}

		.about-intro {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			gap: 1rem;
		}

		.about-details {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			gap: 2.5rem;
		}
		
		.section-divider {
			margin: 2.5rem 0;
		}
	}
</style>